this time all folder and files save in Volumes EMC in docker .... no shared laptop 

1- create volume and save file into
docker run -it --name datbase -v NAKIVO:/backup centos bash

nakivo : volume create 
centos : folder get in systeme > ls


2- can use this Volumes with ather Conatiers 
docker run -it --name mysql -v NAKIVO:/data1 centos bash

3- all data of all thos caoanters save in one volume nakivo
